TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT FP.ITEM_ID, FP.CURRENCY, FP.SAP_WHOLESALE_PRICE, FP.START_DATE, FP.END_DATE, FP.DELETION_INDICATOR, FP.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID FROM (select rank() over (partition by sic.sap_company_code, si.item_id, sic.start_date order by deletion_indicator nulls last, SIC.grid_value nulls last ) as process_priority ,si.item_id , SIC.CURRENCY, SIC.SAP_WHOLESALE_PRICE, SIC.START_DATE, SIC.END_DATE, SIC.DELETION_INDICATOR, FBSH.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID from stg_sap_item_cost SIC ,FCST_BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY FBSH, STYLE_MASTER_1 SM ,slba_item SI ,SAP_ITEM SAP WHERE SIC.PRICE_LIST IS NULL AND SIC.SOLDTO IS NULL AND SIC.MATERIAL_NUM = SI.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM and nvl(SIC.GRID_VALUE,SI.SAP_GRID_VALUE)=SI.SAP_GRID_VALUE AND SI.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM=SAP.MATERIAL_NUM AND SI.SAP_GRID_VALUE=SAP.GRID_VALUE AND SAP.MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE!='99' AND SI.putup_code='000' AND SM.style_num = SI.style_num AND SM.division_group=SI.division_group AND nvl(trim(si.company_code),'--')=sm.company_code AND FBSH.STRATEGIC_BUSINESS_UNIT_DESC = SM.SBU_DESC)FP WHERE FP.PROCESS_PRIORITY=1
